#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine_similarity.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine\\_similarity"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:1 of
msgid "Compute cosine similarity between samples in X and Y."
msgstr "计算 X 和 Y 中样本之间的余弦相似度。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:3 of
msgid ""
"Cosine similarity, or the cosine kernel, computes similarity as the "
"normalized dot product of X and Y:"
msgstr "余弦相似度或余弦核，将相似度计算为 X 和 Y 的归一化点积："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:6 of
msgid "K(X, Y) = <X, Y> / (||X||*||Y||)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:8 of
msgid "On L2-normalized data, this function is equivalent to linear_kernel."
msgstr "在 L2 归一化数据上，此函数等价于 linear_kernel。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:10 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <cosine_similarity>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <cosine_similarity>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine_similarity.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:12 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:14 of
msgid ""
"Input data. If ``None``, the output will be the pairwise similarities "
"between all samples in ``X``."
msgstr "输入数据。如果为 ``None``，则输出将是 ``X`` 中所有样本之间的两两相似度。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:17 of
msgid ""
"Whether to return dense output even when the input is sparse. If "
"``False``, the output is sparse if both input tensors are sparse."
msgstr ""
"即使输入是稀疏的，是否也返回密集输出。如果为 ``False``，则当两个输入张量"
"都为稀疏时，输出也为稀疏。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine_similarity.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine.cosine_similarity:21 of
msgid "**kernel matrix** -- A tensor with shape (n_samples_X, n_samples_Y)."
msgstr "**核矩阵** -- 一个形状为 (n_samples_X, n_samples_Y) 的张量。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.cosine_similarity.rst
msgid "返回类型"
